      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i just landed in dubai from a 14 hour flight and my chest feels really sharp and painful whenever i breathe in deep. i'm also kinda short of breath. i've been super stressed with work lately and the travel was intense... u think i'm just having a panic attack or something? it's making me feel really weird.",
