      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i've had anxiety before and this feels a bit like that, just way more intense because of the travel. i don't really want to go to an emergency room in a foreign country if i don't have to, it seems like a lot of trouble. do u think it's safe to just head back to my hotel, take some extra sleep, and maybe some herbal tea to calm down? i'm sure it's just the jet lag and the stress catching up to me.",
